Lumina Privacy Policy
Last updated: February 2026

Summary: Lumina is an educational calculator tool. We do NOT collect, store, or transmit any personal data.
1. What is Lumina?
Lumina is a free browser extension that provides an educational position size calculator and economic calendar overlay for TradingView. It is designed for learning purposes only.

2. Data Collection
We do NOT collect any data. Specifically:

No personal information is collected
No browsing history is tracked
No financial data is stored
No cookies are used for tracking
No data is sent to external servers (except Investing.com for calendar data)
3. Local Storage
The extension uses your browser's local storage only to save:

Your theme preference (light/dark)
Cached calendar data for faster loading
This data stays on your device and is never transmitted.

4. Third-Party Services
The extension fetches public economic calendar data from Investing.com. This is read-only data and no personal information is shared with this service.

5. Permissions
The extension requires:

TradingView.com access: To display the calculator overlay on TradingView charts
Storage: To save your local preferences
6. Educational Disclaimer
This extension is for educational purposes only. It does not:

Execute trades
Connect to any brokerage
Provide financial advice
Handle real money
7. Contact
For questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please open an issue on our GitHub repository or contact us via the extension store listing.
